   License    : W3 LICENSE (web content accessibility use)

   The following file is reproduced unmodified from the apca-w3 package:
     src/apca-w3.js

   Used for predicting perceptual contrast for web content per WCAG
   guidelines. The W3 license permits royalty-free use for this purpose.
